56
00:04:49,533 --> 00:04:54,433
and took the country, really,
from the 19th century

57
00:04:54,467 --> 00:04:58,733
into the 20th century
very, very quickly.

58
00:04:58,767 --> 00:05:00,433
Absolutely.
His Majesty took over

59
00:05:00,467 --> 00:05:04,133
