487
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:54,267
Now, in the beginning
it was fishermen.

488
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:56,633
- Yeah.
- But then, start to trade

489
00:29:56,667 --> 00:29:59,433
all up and down East Africa,
Iran, Pakistan,

490
00:29:59,467 --> 00:30:01,767
